gate.lib.interaction.process

Class Process4StringStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • gate.lib.interaction.process.ProcessBase
      • gate.lib.interaction.process.Process4StringStream

  • public class Process4StringStream
extends ProcessBase
    Minimalist class for exchanging String lines This just sends or retrieves arbitrary lines of String which could be JSON we already have or want to parse ourself, or anything else. Note: the string being sent over this connection in either direction should NOT contain any newline character! NOTE: at the moment, reading from the process can block forever, there is no timeout!
